# =============================================================================
# OLAKE - Locket Secrets Template
# =============================================================================
# Template file for Locket secret injection.
# Uses Infisical references (infisical:///<SECRET_KEY>).
#
# USAGE:
#   locket exec --provider infisical \
#     --connect.host http://132.145.27.89:8080 \
#     --connect.token-file /path/to/token \
#     --env-file secrets.env \
#     -- docker compose -f compose.yaml up -d
#
# NOTE: Olake uses JSON config files mounted at ./drivers/mongodb/examples/.
# Connection secrets (MongoDB URI, destination credentials, etc.) should be
# stored in those config files rather than as environment variables.
# If environment-based secrets are needed in future, add them below.
# =============================================================================